# MemorIAmobile — environment overview
# This monorepo does NOT use a single root .env for runtime.
# Copy each app example below:

# 1) API (Express + MySQL)
#    apps/api/.env.example  ->  apps/api/.env
#    Needs: MYSQL_*, JWT_SECRET, PORT, CORS_ORIGIN
#    Optional: GOOGLE_*, APPLE_*, ECOMMERCE_*, INTEGRATED_AI_*, WEBSITE_*

# 2) Web (Vite)
#    apps/web/.env.example  ->  apps/web/.env
#    Optional: API_PROXY_TARGET (default http://127.0.0.1:3001)

# After filling secrets:
#   npm run migrate
#   npm run dev
#
# Expected local ports:
#   Web  http://localhost:3000
#   API  http://localhost:3001
#
# Auth and data go through /hcgi/api (MySQL). PocketBase is not used.
